{
  "name": "Pinterest WF3 - Verify Published",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Pinterest – Workflow 3: Verify published pins (daily)\n\nReads rows where **Status = Scheduled** (with a Tailwind Post ID), calls Tailwind **Get Post**, and when the post is **published** (status = sent), writes the real **Pinterest URL** into **Pin URL** and sets **Status = Published** + actual **Pinned Time**.\n\n**Setup:** Google Sheets + Tailwind (Bearer) credentials; accountId in Set Config.",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "f655c399-06d4-460a-909f-615906a6a447",
      "name": "README",
